ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectParc Downsview Park Inc.
PrecisOrder (1) approving PARC DOWNSVIEW PARK INC.'s (PDP) 2011-2012 to 2015-2016 Corporate Plan; (2) authorizing the disposal of 16.2 acres of real property held by PDP in the Stanley Greene Neighbourhood to Urbancorp Dowsview Park Development Inc., Toronto, Ontario, and the retention and use of proceeds of the disposal; (3) authorizing PDP to enter into a land lease for 14.0 acres with Maple Leaf Sports & Entertainment Ltd., Toronto, Ontario; (4) authorizing PDP to enter into a land lease for approximately 4.0 acres with Buckingham Sports, Toronto, Ontario; (5) authorizing PDP to release a restrictive covenant on a parcel of land in exchange of another parcel of land owned by Bombardier Aerospace.
